---
// About / welcome band. Static content.
---

<section id="about" class="border-t border-black/[0.08] bg-white">
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-[1000px] px-8 py-20 text-center max-[960px]:px-6">
		<div class="mb-[18px] font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-brand">Welcome to Elevate Ballers</div>
		<h2 class="mb-6 font-display text-[clamp(34px,4.5vw,56px)] uppercase leading-[0.95] text-ink">Your home for the game<br />we live for</h2>
		<p class="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-[640px] text-[17px] leading-[1.7] text-muted">
			The official home of Kenya's premier basketball league. Follow every game, every team, and every player. Standings update after every match, and the Player of the Week highlights one standout performance from the past week.
		</p>
		<a href="/about-club" class="inline-block rounded border border-black/20 px-[30px] py-[15px] text-[14px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.04em] text-ink2 no-underline hover:border-brand hover:text-brand">Read the full story →</a>
	</div>
</section>
